//
// #Information
//

//
// Spacer mixin:
// is more flexibile, you can get a fixed value from just adding
// a number that will get multiplied automtically with the base set number.
//
// Example:
// 
// spacerNum * 2 = 60
// spacerNum * .5 = 15
// spacerNum * .25 = 7.5
//

-spacer(n)
	spacerNum * n

spacerNumMobile = defaultNum / 2

